                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13142.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13142.htm">成功無短路 [ SÊNG-KONG BÔ TÉ-LŌ͘ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">成功無短路
 　　「彼時耶穌予聖神chhōa到曠野，欲受魔鬼試。」　馬太4章1節。
　　欲造成品性，無有近&ecirc;路；&agrave;i得著近路&ecirc;，攏是做誘惑&ecirc;根源。亞當kap夏娃論in &ecirc;智慧&ecirc;發達是親像囡仔。對佇食果子，in想隨時&agrave;i欲得著彼个智慧。智慧是好&ecirc;物，猶久袂會佇一時陣來得著。智慧是親像一个媠&ecirc;記念塔，起佇忍耐、勞苦&ecirc;地基頂。亞當kap夏娃行短&ecirc;路&agrave;i欲得著智慧，反轉續陷落罪。
　　主&ecirc;受試猶原有相同&ecirc;教示佇teh。「人會...<a href="artical-13142.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baad3faee84e.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baad3faee84e.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13143.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13143.htm">神Ê軟chiá? [ SÎN Ê NŃG-CHIÁⁿ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">神&Ecirc;軟chi&aacute;ⁿ
 　　咱基督徒所信&ecirc;神是真軟chi&aacute;ⁿ &ecirc;神－據在人侮辱；予對敵歹款待，無ke講一句話，也無想欲報仇；尚且佇十字架頂來受見笑&ecirc;死。
　　無親像thang驚惶&ecirc;鬼將軍teh處治伊&ecirc;對敵，彼款&ecirc;神；也無親像大膽&ecirc;外科醫，無想患者&ecirc;艱苦，直刣、直割。反轉n&aacute;家己予人割&ecirc;款，會感著別人&ecirc;艱苦。
　　伊無親像強摃，摃破咱&ecirc;心門，強強入來。伊&ecirc;身軀予露水沃澹，徛佇門口teh細聲叫。伊無捲...<a href="artical-13143.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baad3222c02a.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baad3222c02a.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-劉約翰/Lâu Iok-hān]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13146.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13146.htm">基督教做成功Ê要素 [ KI-TOK-KÀU CHOÈ SÊNG-KONG Ê IÀU-SÒ͘ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">基督教做成功&Ecirc;要素
　　深理kap淺理是對反，能力kap人力也無相同。求世界&ecirc;智慧是用人力，求靈界&ecirc;智慧是用靈力－就是用誠心祈禱得著神&ecirc;啟示－。小智慧是先知後來行，大智慧是先行後來知。求智慧時刻毋敢離開我，離開我就無主；信神時刻毋敢有我，就無神。所以人理是淺--&ecirc;，天理是深--&ecirc;；淺理用智，深理用信。
　　神kap人是相幫贊&ecirc;，神用人&ecirc;身軀來顯出道理人倚靠人&ecirc;力來成事。人&ecirc;力已經盡，靈&ecirc;力就來－哥林多後書12:9－10－盡力是人&ecirc;本份。職份&eci...<a href="artical-13146.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/49f56fe3b6f09.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/49f56fe3b6f09.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1926-1 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-李水車/Lí Chuí-chhia]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src13147.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13147.htm">著學蚼蟻 [ TIO̍H O̍H KÁU-HIĀ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">著學蚼蟻
 　　貪憚&ecirc;人ah！啥事毋看蚼蟻來學伊&ecirc;智慧！」箴言6:6.
　　所羅門是智識&ecirc;人，伊叫人著學蚼蟻&ecirc;智慧。蚼蟻是至細&ecirc;動物，有啥物thang予咱學，有深深&ecirc;意思佇teh。照現時&ecirc;動物學者teh研究蚼蟻，論伊&ecirc;家庭逐項有次序、有房間、有粟倉；會相刣，也有嫁娶。若看樹頂&ecirc;蚼蟻岫，就知實在真有智慧，逐項真堅固，親像炮台&ecirc;款。蚼蟻有啥物智慧？斟酌來想幾若款：－
　　1. 蚼蟻&ecirc;勤儉。
　　a. 蚼蟻&ecirc;骨力。逐日勤勤做工，暗時也做無煞。論伊&e...<a href="artical-13147.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
